channel.title: Demonik Coders<3
channel.description:
[b]CLOSED[/b] --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Alright. Well people know me for several reasons, mostly because of my RscReloaded Server that I used to run.
Well, it got shutdown a long time ago due to my other coder adding a botnet to the client, so it got shutdown. Well i shut it down myself due do this.
Well, I am thinking of bringing it back up now. I coded ALOT of new things in it.
I took out k\d Ratios Clan chats Auto Client Updater etc etc. And all of that for now because I might add it in later for future updates instead.
But my RscReloaded Server, this one has never been released or leaked like the other one has which was a very old version (2 Years or so).
This one has practically every bug\dupe fixed. There's just a few more bugs that I need to fix which I am working on now.
I am looking for some people who would like to join in on this project.
You [b]must[/b] be familiar with the Demonik Source.
Coders: Anc13nts - Me Someone
Xml Editors: Ecstacy
Website Designer: Anc13nts - Me Someone
I am not asking for help at all on how to do this stuff, I can do this all for my self if I want to It does not bother me. I am just seeing if people would like to join so I don't have to do it all my self because it will take up to much time.
I have made quite a few layouts for RscR if you have seen the past websites for it. But inorder to be in it. You must know how to code. Obviously.
You must be familiar with Demonik (I'll make sure by asking you questions about it)
Add me at keithamunoz@hotmail.com - Msn
And you must reply on here as well.
